    "description": "Kreeps is a tower defense game where you choose how your towers and the enemies scale as the game progresses.<br><br><strong>Choose your path</strong><br>At the end of each wave the player makes 3 choices:<br><br><strong>1. Select a location</strong><br>Location choices give all Kreeps a permanent buff and also extend the path. These buffs stack as the game progresses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/03377fda788d9b3a3b2532d1946268ce.avif?t=1771560189\" width=540 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>2. Select a Kreep</strong><br>Kreep choices are added to each following wave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/6b4eb65418ce725149d4582be255246c.avif?t=1771560189\" width=540 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>3. Select a shop card</strong><br>The shop provides the choice of a weapon to purchase, 3 random free upgrades, or the choice of extra gold. Only 1 can be selected each wave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/b41cd31269bb886c788330cc7b66132d.avif?t=1771560189\" width=540 height=160 /></span><br><br>Choose from 7 different types of towers and weapons each with their own unique upgrades for a variety of strategies to choose from.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/ddebfe7378c4efbcd30a6fa773b439a8.webp?t=1771560189\" width=420 height=60 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/7739363855071713ca41c1fa9a82990b.avif?t=1771560189\" width=476 height=68 /></span><br><br>There are 6 different types of Kreeps each with their own weakness. Choose carefully.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351570/extras/ce58ba26eacdfd09df3487f9a4d7e91c.avif?t=1771560189\" width=432 height=64 /></span>",
